  m_Name: Slide_02_Currency
  m_EditorClassIdentifier:
  title: "Dead Samurai Carry No Coin"
  body: "Every enemy you kill drops currency. But that money isn\u2019t yours until
    you extract.\n\nReach the extraction zone and hold E for 10 seconds to secure
    your loot. If you die before extracting, you lose everything earned that raid.
    No exceptions.\n\nExtract often. Greed kills."
